description:
This is a 50 minute workout called 'Rito to Hateno - Morning Easy Run - BotW Treadmill Run Along' from the channel Video Game Run Club.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Mindful Walk and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Run with Link as they do an easy morning run from Rito Village to Hateno Ancient Tech Lab.
